@keepITCore_HostAddress = http://localhost:5025
@email = alice@example.com
@password = Sup3rSecret!

### Register
POST {{keepITCore_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "{{email}}", "password": "{{password}}", "displayName": "Alice" }

### Login (sets the refresh cookie)
POST {{keepITCore_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "{{email}}", "password": "{{password}}" }

### Current user (paste the access token)
GET {{keepITCore_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>

### Refresh (uses the refresh cookie)
POST {{keepITCore_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh

### Logout
POST {{keepITCore_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout

###
